description:
Darkness Radio presents:  Supernatural News/Parashare: The Headless Podcast By The Railroad Tracks Edition!

It has been a crazy wee filled with Aliens, Animals and Headless Stuff and oh, yeah! We brought back an old friend, Darkness Radio Alumni, Jessica Freeburg! 

In today's show, forget doctors, Uri Gellar says Aliens are coming to cure our diseases!  The Romans and the Merovingians both have horses and skeletons missing their heads in England!  Fish are talkin' and mad beat boxin', yo! and Jessica tells us how she prefers to be BBQ as opposed to soup! 

Check out Jessica's latest projects here:  https://jessicafreeburg.com/
